{"tid":2363922,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"震驚 !!! 雲狗爾 14 世界盃換籠戰術竟然被人揭發係抄 95 皇朝盃 中國 隊教練 戚務生 !!!","createTime":"2021-01-12T14:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T05:31:05.000Z","uid":124655,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18f48a3aab9aaba7b5b99d5f16858118a5b20c81","tid":2363922,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:36:46.000Z","msg":"14 世界盃 雲狗爾 係唔知邊場臨尾換 籠門 踢十二碼大戰, 被譽為神級戰術調動, 不過, 有留意不同時空既我, 終於發現原來雲狗爾呢招係抄 95 年皇朝盃中國隊教練 戚務生 既戰術 !!!<br />\n<br />\n時為 95 年皇朝盃季軍賽 中國 對 香港,<br />\n香港隊雖然一面倒佔儘優勢, 將中國踢到 on99, 但運氣稍遜下, 賽事進入十二碼大戰,<br />\n而係法定時間完之前, 戚務生 竟然換走表現優異, 勇救咗無數咁多必入球既 區楚良, 換入寂寂無名既守門員 孫剛, 到底呢場十二碼大戰最後發展成點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家一齊去片 !!!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OSfMeapuz_c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOSfMeapuz_c&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJufkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=1663c805\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OSfMeapuz_c</a>"},{"pid":"07fe52ea454d23340af101da1e4ce14b2885bfcf","tid":2363922,"uid":124655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:56:17.000Z","msg":"當年足總, 港隊, 全港市民 非常團結萬衆一心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/82xcXFXdsZ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F82xcXFXdsZ0&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJufkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=aa6428e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/82xcXFXdsZ0</a>"},{"pid":"50d867f738b73c3da84b285bc28839f9591cc2fe","tid":2363922,"uid":158755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T18:11:43.000Z","msg":"港聯個龍係邊個<br />\n屌你勁撚到"},{"pid":"be395553c62f2eefd4628db90e92d31b87c66835","tid":2363922,"uid":320041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50d867f738b73c3da84b285bc28839f9591cc2fe","tid":2363922,"uid":158755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTi